{"tid":2303606,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共和黨撕裂恐失參院優勢","createTime":"2020-11-28T05:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T07:25:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"35bb6e5fedf5b5add395977aa42959d9ccd9cdca","tid":2303606,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:53:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201128/4HO4GTY72BG4PFKXAZ6ZHICVQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201128%2F4HO4GTY72BG4PFKXAZ6ZHICVQQ%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7Cpj7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=e8fbdd35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201128%2F4HO4GTY72BG4PFKXAZ6ZHICVQQ%2F&h=da6b23c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201128/4HO4GTY72BG4PFKXAZ6ZHICVQQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n共和黨撕裂恐失參院優勢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JEQvYca0Cru4cjQczAv3fYGsnLE=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/56V7LATDZ5HY7MKJVTZTKQKWDY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJEQvYca0Cru4cjQczAv3fYGsnLE%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F56V7LATDZ5HY7MKJVTZTKQKWDY.jpg&h=fcccc118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■喬治亞州應特朗普陣營要求再次重新點票仍在進行中。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普連任失敗幾成定局，共和黨接下來要在來年1月進行次輪選舉的兩個喬治亞州參院議席保住最少一席，才可保住參院優勢。可是，共和黨正為投票系統是否公正陷於撕裂，或令民主黨得益。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：倘選舉人團確認拜登當選  特朗普稱會離開白宮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n候選人陷兩難<br />\n<br />\n共和黨在喬州參院選戰面對的兩難局面，是大選在該州落敗的特朗普一方面指控投票系統不可靠，但另方面兩位競逐連任的共和黨員珀杜（David Perdue）和洛夫勒（Kelly Loeffler）要選民兩個月後使用同一系統投票給自己，似乎欠說服力，黨友亦意見不一。<br />\n<br />\n阿特蘭大律師兼特朗普親信伍德就要求共和黨支持者抵制投票系統，辯稱選民必要時可手寫投票，並譴責珀杜和洛夫勒為特朗普做得不夠。喬州州務卿拉芬斯珀格則質疑有些人不面對現實，認為即使選民以缺席投票方式參與，選票都避不過要經系統掃描。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陰謀論律師入稟挑戰結果<br />\n<br />\n珀杜和洛夫勒雖曾要。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國《華盛頓郵報》"},{"pid":"a20e0f6bcc147e988baed9aac80a409bb5351c22","tid":2303606,"uid":286897,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"847c9fc03a4871813510504a9a1a1c9a2863c4b3","tid":2303606,"uid":127575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:59:54.000Z","msg":"華盛頓郵報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00eb9cfba0dee5a78c9689e5f9cf0cfc7d96f073","tid":2303606,"uid":371606,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拜登個屎眼就撕裂<br />\n準備坐監啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdcd8ab5f0227479cd166220d4c4a0136e63545","tid":2303606,"uid":221171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67zNNpB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67zNNpB.jpg&h=2d8b3a87&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}